FBIS4-27986 "dreas109_a_94010" FBIS-EAS-94-109 Daily Report 5 Jun 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA Japan Peruvian President Arrives for Four-Day Visit Peruvian President Arrives for Four-Day Visit OW0506071794 Tokyo KYODO in English 0704 GMT 5 Jun 94 OW0506071794 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Narita, Chiba Pref., June 5 KYODO -- Peruvian President Alberto Fujimori arrived in Narita Sunday [5 June] afternoon for a four-day visit to Japan on his way to China. Fujimori is scheduled to hold talks with Prime Minister Tsutomu Hata on Monday night, government officials said. It was the fifth time for Fujimori to visit Japan, including the 1990 visit just before he became president. He will make an official visit to China from June 8-12.
